@* 告警事件清單:由 SignalR 即時推播累積(狀態升級/恢復各記一筆),清單由 panels.js 維護。 *@
<section class="alerts" aria-label="告警事件清單">
    <div class="alerts__head">
        <h2 class="alerts__title">告警事件<span class="alerts__count" id="alert-count" aria-label="事件筆數">0</span></h2>
        <button type="button" id="alert-clear" class="btn-ghost">清除</button>
    </div>
    <ul class="alert-list" id="alert-list" aria-live="polite">
        <li class="alert-empty">尚無告警事件</li>
    </ul>
</section>
